empty or invalid
`ConstantRangeList` being
passed to
`ConstantRangeList::inser
t`.\n\n4. **Proposed Edit
Points**:\n   - Modify
the `GetConstantIntRange`
lambda (lines 675-683 in
`llvm/lib/Transforms/IPO/
FunctionAttrs.cpp`) to
handle non-`ConstantInt`
values gracefully.
